text: Cecil J. Toor (July 28, 1895 – May 23, 1969) was an American football coach. He served as the head football coach at Delaware Valley College in 1922. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1895 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Delaware Valley Aggies football coaches Category:Sportspeople from Philadelphia Category:Players of American football from Pennsylvania
